## 🗄️ Database Schema

### Tables

#### `skills`
```sql
CREATE TABLE skills (
  id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
  name TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  category TEXT NOT NULL,
  description TEXT,
  tags_json TEXT,      -- JSON array
  triggers_json TEXT   -- JSON array
)
```

#### `skill_cards`
```sql
CREATE TABLE skill_cards (
  skill_id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY REFERENCES skills(id),
  use_when_json TEXT,
  avoid_when_json TEXT,
  inputs TEXT,
  outputs TEXT,
  activation TEXT,
  similar_json TEXT,
  diff_notes TEXT,
  risk_level TEXT
)
```

#### `skills_fts`
```sql
CREATE VIRTUAL TABLE skills_fts USING fts5(
  name,
  description,
  triggers,
  tags
)
```

