## 🔧 Troubleshooting

### Database not found
```bash
npm run init-db
```

### FTS index corrupted
```bash
npm run reindex
```

### Port 3000 in use
```bash
PORT=3001 npm run dev
```

### Search not working
Check FTS index:
```bash
sqlite3 data/skills.db "SELECT COUNT(*) FROM skills_fts;"
```

